{
  "video_id": "AyWtIwwEgS0",
  "title": "The next manufacturing revolution is here | Olivier Scalabre",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13734.0,
      "end_time": 16294.0,
      "text": "Guys, we have an issue."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16294.0,
      "end_time": 17416.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17416.0,
      "end_time": 21136.0,
      "text": "Growth is fading away, and it's a big deal."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21136.0,
      "end_time": 24018.0,
      "text": "Our global economy stops growing."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 24018.0,
      "end_time": 25441.0,
      "text": "And it's not new."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 25441.0,
      "end_time": 29213.0,
      "text": "Growth has actually declined for the last 50 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 29213.0,
      "end_time": 31777.0,
      "text": "If we continue like this, we need to learn"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 31777.0,
      "end_time": 36249.0,
      "text": "how to live in a world with no growth in the next decade."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 36249.0,
      "end_time": 39750.0,
      "text": "This is scary because when the economy doesn't grow,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 39750.0,
      "end_time": 42535.0,
      "text": "our children don't get better lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 42535.0,
      "end_time": 45972.0,
      "text": "What's even scarier is that when the pie does not grow,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 45972.0,
      "end_time": 47552.0,
      "text": "each of us get a smaller piece."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 47552.0,
      "end_time": 50070.0,
      "text": "We're then ready to fight for a bigger one."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 50070.0,
      "end_time": 53585.0,
      "text": "This creates tensions and serious conflicts."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 53585.0,
      "end_time": 57350.0,
      "text": "Growth matters a lot."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 57350.0,
      "end_time": 59662.0,
      "text": "If we look at the history of growth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 59662.0,
      "end_time": 62198.0,
      "text": "times of big growth have always been fueled"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 62198.0,
      "end_time": 64818.0,
      "text": "by big manufacturing revolutions."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 64818.0,
      "end_time": 68419.0,
      "text": "It happened three times, every 50-60 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 68419.0,
      "end_time": 72467.0,
      "text": "The steam engine in the middle of the 19th century,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 72467.0,
      "end_time": 76252.0,
      "text": "the mass-production model in the beginning of the 20th century --"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 76252.0,
      "end_time": 78384.0,
      "text": "thanks, Mr. Ford."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 78384.0,
      "end_time": 82157.0,
      "text": "And the first automation wave in the 1970s."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 82157.0,
      "end_time": 84377.0,
      "text": "Why did these manufacturing revolutions"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 84377.0,
      "end_time": 87677.0,
      "text": "create huge growth in our economies?"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 87677.0,
      "end_time": 91591.0,
      "text": "Because they have injected huge productivity improvement."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 91591.0,
      "end_time": 93080.0,
      "text": "It's rather simple:"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 93080.0,
      "end_time": 96339.0,
      "text": "in order to grow, you need to be producing more,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 96339.0,
      "end_time": 99241.0,
      "text": "putting more into our economy."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 99241.0,
      "end_time": 104877.0,
      "text": "This means either more labor or more capital or more productivity."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 104877.0,
      "end_time": 109744.0,
      "text": "Each time, productivity has been the growth lever."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 109744.0,
      "end_time": 112511.0,
      "text": "I'm here today to tell you"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 112511.0,
      "end_time": 116245.0,
      "text": "that we are on the verge of another huge change,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 116245.0,
      "end_time": 119731.0,
      "text": "and that this change, surprisingly enough,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 119731.0,
      "end_time": 123394.0,
      "text": "is going to come from manufacturing, again."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 123394.0,
      "end_time": 126526.0,
      "text": "It will get us out of our growth slump"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 126526.0,
      "end_time": 130394.0,
      "text": "and it will change radically the way globalization has been shaped"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 130394.0,
      "end_time": 131935.0,
      "text": "over the last decade."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 131935.0,
      "end_time": 137230.0,
      "text": "I'm here to tell you about the amazing fourth manufacturing revolution"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 137230.0,
      "end_time": 139213.0,
      "text": "that is currently underway."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 139213.0,
      "end_time": 141698.0,
      "text": "It's not as if we've done nothing with manufacturing"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 141698.0,
      "end_time": 143011.0,
      "text": "since the last revolution."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 143011.0,
      "end_time": 145450.0,
      "text": "Actually, we've made some pretty lame attempts"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 145450.0,
      "end_time": 147075.0,
      "text": "to try to revitalize it."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 147075.0,
      "end_time": 150076.0,
      "text": "But none of them have been the big overhaul"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 150076.0,
      "end_time": 152384.0,
      "text": "we really need to get us growing again."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 152384.0,
      "end_time": 157002.0,
      "text": "For example, we've tried to relocate our factories offshore"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 157002.0,
      "end_time": 161048.0,
      "text": "in order to reduce cost and take advantage of cheap labor."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 161048.0,
      "end_time": 164655.0,
      "text": "Not only did this not inspire productivity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 164655.0,
      "end_time": 167151.0,
      "text": "but it only saved money for a short period of time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 167151.0,
      "end_time": 170455.0,
      "text": "because cheap labor didn't stay cheap for long."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 170455.0,
      "end_time": 174401.0,
      "text": "Then, we've tried to make our factories larger"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 174401.0,
      "end_time": 177318.0,
      "text": "and we specialized them by product."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 177318.0,
      "end_time": 180655.0,
      "text": "The idea was that we can make a lot of one product"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 180655.0,
      "end_time": 184022.0,
      "text": "and stockpile it to be sold with demand."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 184022.0,
      "end_time": 186625.0,
      "text": "This did help productivity for a while."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 186625.0,
      "end_time": 191432.0,
      "text": "But it introduced a lot of rigidities in our supply chain."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 191432.0,
      "end_time": 193232.0,
      "text": "Let's take fashion retail."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 193232.0,
      "end_time": 195374.0,
      "text": "Traditional clothing companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 195374.0,
      "end_time": 200787.0,
      "text": "have built offshore, global, rigid supply chains."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 200787.0,
      "end_time": 203562.0,
      "text": "When fast-fashion competitors like Zara"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 203562.0,
      "end_time": 206097.0,
      "text": "started replenishing their stocks faster"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 206097.0,
      "end_time": 209800.0,
      "text": "from two collections a year to one collection a month,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 209800.0,
      "end_time": 212368.0,
      "text": "none of them has been able to keep up with the pace."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 212368.0,
      "end_time": 216008.0,
      "text": "Most of them are in great difficulties today."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 216008.0,
      "end_time": 219236.0,
      "text": "Yet, with all of their shortcomings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 219236.0,
      "end_time": 221539.0,
      "text": "those are the factories we know today."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 221539.0,
      "end_time": 223181.0,
      "text": "When you open the doors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 223181.0,
      "end_time": 226396.0,
      "text": "they look the same as they did 50 years ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 226396.0,
      "end_time": 232273.0,
      "text": "We've just changed the location, the size, the way they operate."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 232273.0,
      "end_time": 234641.0,
      "text": "Can you name anything else that looks the same"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 234641.0,
      "end_time": 236220.0,
      "text": "as it did 50 years ago?"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 236220.0,
      "end_time": 237836.0,
      "text": "It's crazy."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 237836.0,
      "end_time": 240892.0,
      "text": "We've made all the tweaks to the model that we could,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 240892.0,
      "end_time": 245032.0,
      "text": "and now we hit its limits."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 245032.0,
      "end_time": 249893.0,
      "text": "After all of our attempts to fix the manufacturing model failed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 249893.0,
      "end_time": 252722.0,
      "text": "we thought growth could come from elsewhere."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 252722.0,
      "end_time": 254786.0,
      "text": "We turned to the tech sector --"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 254786.0,
      "end_time": 257178.0,
      "text": "there's been quite a lot of innovations there."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 257178.0,
      "end_time": 259906.0,
      "text": "Just to name one: the Internet."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 259906.0,
      "end_time": 261735.0,
      "text": "We hoped it could produce growth."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 261735.0,
      "end_time": 264251.0,
      "text": "And indeed, it changed our lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 264251.0,
      "end_time": 269081.0,
      "text": "It made big waves in the media, the service, the entertainment spaces."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 269081.0,
      "end_time": 272011.0,
      "text": "But it hasn't done much for productivity."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 272011.0,
      "end_time": 276331.0,
      "text": "Actually, what's surprising is that productivity is on the decline"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 276331.0,
      "end_time": 279523.0,
      "text": "despite all of those innovation efforts."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 279523.0,
      "end_time": 283305.0,
      "text": "Imagine that -- sitting at work, scrolling through Facebook,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 283305.0,
      "end_time": 287133.0,
      "text": "watching videos on YouTube has made us less productive."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 287133.0,
      "end_time": 288308.0,
      "text": "Weird."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 288308.0,
      "end_time": 289916.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 289916.0,
      "end_time": 292580.0,
      "text": "This is why we are not growing."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 292580.0,
      "end_time": 295880.0,
      "text": "We failed at reinventing the manufacturing space,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 295880.0,
      "end_time": 301184.0,
      "text": "and large technological innovations have played away from it."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 301184.0,
      "end_time": 303927.0,
      "text": "But what if we could combine those forces?"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 303927.0,
      "end_time": 308819.0,
      "text": "What if the existing manufacturing and large technological innovation"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 308819.0,
      "end_time": 313406.0,
      "text": "came together to create the next big manufacturing reinvention."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 313406.0,
      "end_time": 314688.0,
      "text": "Bingo!"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 314688.0,
      "end_time": 317195.0,
      "text": "This is the fourth manufacturing revolution,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 317195.0,
      "end_time": 319355.0,
      "text": "and it's happening right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 319355.0,
      "end_time": 322645.0,
      "text": "Major technologies are entering the manufacturing space,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 322645.0,
      "end_time": 324316.0,
      "text": "big time."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 324316.0,
      "end_time": 328217.0,
      "text": "They will boost industrial productivity by more than a third."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 328217.0,
      "end_time": 333286.0,
      "text": "This is massive, and it will do a lot in creating growth."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 333286.0,
      "end_time": 336091.0,
      "text": "Let me tell you about some of them."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 336091.0,
      "end_time": 339583.0,
      "text": "Have you already met advanced manufacturing robots?"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 339583.0,
      "end_time": 341702.0,
      "text": "They are the size of humans,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 341702.0,
      "end_time": 343747.0,
      "text": "they actually collaborate with them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 343747.0,
      "end_time": 345350.0,
      "text": "and they can be programmed"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 345350.0,
      "end_time": 349628.0,
      "text": "in order to perform complex, non-repetitive tasks."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 349628.0,
      "end_time": 354590.0,
      "text": "Today in our factories, only 8 percent of the tasks are automated."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 354590.0,
      "end_time": 358551.0,
      "text": "The less complex, the more repetitive ones."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 358551.0,
      "end_time": 361452.0,
      "text": "It will be 25 percent in 10 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 361452.0,
      "end_time": 364289.0,
      "text": "It means that by 2025,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 364289.0,
      "end_time": 366877.0,
      "text": "advanced robots will complement workers"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 366877.0,
      "end_time": 369744.0,
      "text": "to be, together, 20 percent more productive,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 369744.0,
      "end_time": 371769.0,
      "text": "to manufacture 20 percent more outputs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 371769.0,
      "end_time": 375118.0,
      "text": "to achieve 20 percent additional growth."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 375118.0,
      "end_time": 378425.0,
      "text": "This isn't some fancy, futuristic idea."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 378425.0,
      "end_time": 381993.0,
      "text": "These robots are working for us right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 381993.0,
      "end_time": 387563.0,
      "text": "Last year in the US, they helped Amazon prepare and ship all the products"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 387563.0,
      "end_time": 389681.0,
      "text": "required for Cyber Monday,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 389681.0,
      "end_time": 392401.0,
      "text": "the annual peak of online retail."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 392401.0,
      "end_time": 394049.0,
      "text": "Last year in the US,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 394049.0,
      "end_time": 400626.0,
      "text": "it was the biggest online shopping day of the year and of history."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 400626.0,
      "end_time": 404276.0,
      "text": "Consumers spent 3 billion dollars on electronics that day."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 404276.0,
      "end_time": 407502.0,
      "text": "That's real economic growth."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 407502.0,
      "end_time": 411574.0,
      "text": "Then there's additive manufacturing, 3D printing."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 411574.0,
      "end_time": 415606.0,
      "text": "3D printing has already improved plastic manufacturing"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 415606.0,
      "end_time": 418614.0,
      "text": "and it's now making its way through metal."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 418614.0,
      "end_time": 420875.0,
      "text": "Those are not small industries."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 420875.0,
      "end_time": 423915.0,
      "text": "Plastic and metals represent 25 percent"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 423915.0,
      "end_time": 426717.0,
      "text": "of global manufacturing production."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 426717.0,
      "end_time": 429005.0,
      "text": "Let's take a real example."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 429005.0,
      "end_time": 431967.0,
      "text": "In the aerospace industry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 431967.0,
      "end_time": 436484.0,
      "text": "fuel nozzles are some of the most complex parts to manufacture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 436484.0,
      "end_time": 437806.0,
      "text": "for one reason:"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 437806.0,
      "end_time": 441019.0,
      "text": "they are made up of 20 different parts"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 441019.0,
      "end_time": 443854.0,
      "text": "that need to be separately produced"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 443854.0,
      "end_time": 447301.0,
      "text": "and then painstakingly assembled."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 447301.0,
      "end_time": 450451.0,
      "text": "Aerospace companies are now using 3D printing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 450451.0,
      "end_time": 453539.0,
      "text": "which allows them to turn those 20 different parts"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 453539.0,
      "end_time": 455368.0,
      "text": "into just one."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 455368.0,
      "end_time": 456909.0,
      "text": "The results?"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 456909.0,
      "end_time": 459269.0,
      "text": "40 percent more productivity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 459269.0,
      "end_time": 462560.0,
      "text": "40 percent more output produced, 40 percent more growth"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 462560.0,
      "end_time": 465283.0,
      "text": "for this specific industry."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 465283.0,
      "end_time": 471457.0,
      "text": "But actually, the most exciting part of this new manufacturing revolution"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 471457.0,
      "end_time": 474692.0,
      "text": "goes much beyond productivity."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 474692.0,
      "end_time": 478287.0,
      "text": "It's about producing better, smarter products."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 478287.0,
      "end_time": 481099.0,
      "text": "It's about scale customization."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 481099.0,
      "end_time": 485858.0,
      "text": "Imagine a world where you can buy the exact products you want"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 485858.0,
      "end_time": 488092.0,
      "text": "with the functionalities you need,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 488092.0,
      "end_time": 490064.0,
      "text": "with the design you want,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 490064.0,
      "end_time": 491674.0,
      "text": "with the same cost and lead time"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 491674.0,
      "end_time": 493580.0,
      "text": "as a product that's been mass produced,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 493580.0,
      "end_time": 497113.0,
      "text": "like your car, or your clothes or your cell phone."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 497113.0,
      "end_time": 500577.0,
      "text": "The new manufacturing revolution makes it possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 500577.0,
      "end_time": 503422.0,
      "text": "Advanced robots can be programmed"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 503422.0,
      "end_time": 506565.0,
      "text": "in order to perform any product configuration"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 506565.0,
      "end_time": 509791.0,
      "text": "without any setup time or ramp up."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 509791.0,
      "end_time": 515675.0,
      "text": "3D printers instantaneously produce any customized design."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 515674.99999999994,
      "end_time": 521367.99999999994,
      "text": "We are now able to produce a batch of one product, your product,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 521368.00000000006,
      "end_time": 525629.0,
      "text": "at the same cost and lead time as a batch of many."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 525629.0,
      "end_time": 530468.0,
      "text": "Those are only a few examples of the manufacturing revolution at play."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 530468.0,
      "end_time": 534579.0,
      "text": "Not only will manufacturing become more productive,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 534579.0,
      "end_time": 537538.0,
      "text": "it will also become more flexible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 537538.0,
      "end_time": 543106.0,
      "text": "and those were exactly the elements of growth that we are missing."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 543106.0,
      "end_time": 546748.0,
      "text": "But actually, there are even some bigger implications"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 546748.0,
      "end_time": 552441.0,
      "text": "for all of us when manufacturing will find its way back into the limelight."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 552441.0,
      "end_time": 556683.0,
      "text": "It will create a huge macroeconomic shift."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 556683.0,
      "end_time": 561877.0,
      "text": "First, our factories will be relocated into our home markets."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 561877.0,
      "end_time": 564144.0,
      "text": "In the world of scale customization,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 564144.0,
      "end_time": 567722.0,
      "text": "consumer proximity is the new norm."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 567722.0,
      "end_time": 571918.0,
      "text": "Then, our factories will be smaller, agile."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 571918.0,
      "end_time": 575802.0,
      "text": "Scale does not matter anymore, flexibility does."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 575802.0,
      "end_time": 579859.0,
      "text": "They will be operating on a multi-product, made-to-order basis."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 579859.0,
      "end_time": 582590.0,
      "text": "The change will be drastic."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 582590.0,
      "end_time": 587145.0,
      "text": "Globalization will enter a new era."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 587145.0,
      "end_time": 590084.0,
      "text": "The East-to-West trade flows"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 590084.0,
      "end_time": 592789.0,
      "text": "will be replaced by regional trade flows."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 592789.0,
      "end_time": 595687.0,
      "text": "East for East, West for West."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 595687.0,
      "end_time": 597884.0,
      "text": "When you think about that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 597884.0,
      "end_time": 601065.0,
      "text": "the old model was pretty much insane."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 601065.0,
      "end_time": 604840.0,
      "text": "Piling up stocks, making products travel the whole world"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 604840.0,
      "end_time": 606743.0,
      "text": "before they reach their end consumers."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 606743.0,
      "end_time": 611007.0,
      "text": "The new model, producing just next to the consumer market,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 611007.0,
      "end_time": 616678.0,
      "text": "will be much cleaner, much better for our environment."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 616678.0,
      "end_time": 620487.0,
      "text": "In mature economies, manufacturing will be back home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 620487.0,
      "end_time": 622587.0,
      "text": "creating more employment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 622587.0,
      "end_time": 625930.0,
      "text": "more productivity and more growth."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 625930.0,
      "end_time": 628541.0,
      "text": "Good news, isn't it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 628541.0,
      "end_time": 630370.0,
      "text": "But here's the thing with growth --"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 630370.0,
      "end_time": 632328.0,
      "text": "it does not come automatically."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 632328.0,
      "end_time": 635196.0,
      "text": "Mature economies will have to seize it."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 635196.0,
      "end_time": 638547.0,
      "text": "We'll have to massively re-train our workforce."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 638547.0,
      "end_time": 641231.0,
      "text": "In most countries, like in my country, France,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 641231.0,
      "end_time": 644357.0,
      "text": "we've told our children that manufacturing had no future."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 644357.0,
      "end_time": 646358.0,
      "text": "That it was something happening far away."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 646358.0,
      "end_time": 648180.0,
      "text": "We need to reverse that"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 648180.0,
      "end_time": 651203.0,
      "text": "and teach manufacturing again at university."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 651203.0,
      "end_time": 654712.0,
      "text": "Only the countries that will boldly transform"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 654712.0,
      "end_time": 658640.0,
      "text": "will be able to seize this growth."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 658640.0,
      "end_time": 662461.0,
      "text": "It's also a chance for developing economies."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 662461.0,
      "end_time": 666118.0,
      "text": "Of course China and other emerging economies"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 666118.0,
      "end_time": 669545.0,
      "text": "won't be the factory of the world anymore."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 669545.0,
      "end_time": 674187.0,
      "text": "Actually, it was not a sustainable model in the long term,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 674187.0,
      "end_time": 677779.0,
      "text": "as those countries are becoming richer."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 677779.0,
      "end_time": 682827.0,
      "text": "Last year, it was already as expensive to produce in Brazil"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 682827.0,
      "end_time": 686184.0,
      "text": "as to produce in France."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 686184.0,
      "end_time": 693350.0,
      "text": "By 2018, manufacturing costs in China will be on par with the US."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 693350.0,
      "end_time": 695625.0,
      "text": "The new manufacturing revolution"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 695625.0,
      "end_time": 700429.0,
      "text": "will accelerate the transition of those emerging economies"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 700429.0,
      "end_time": 703675.0,
      "text": "towards a model driven by domestic consumption."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 703675.0,
      "end_time": 704876.0,
      "text": "And this is good,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 704876.0,
      "end_time": 707915.0,
      "text": "because this is where growth will be created."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 707915.0,
      "end_time": 709543.0,
      "text": "In the next five years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 709543.0,
      "end_time": 714871.0,
      "text": "the next billion consumers in China will inject more growth in our economies"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 714871.0,
      "end_time": 719944.0,
      "text": "than the top five European markets together."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 719944.0,
      "end_time": 725046.0,
      "text": "This fourth manufacturing revolution is a chance for all of us."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 725046.0,
      "end_time": 727024.0,
      "text": "If we play it right,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 727024.0,
      "end_time": 730969.0,
      "text": "we'll see sustainable growth in all of our economies."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 730969.0,
      "end_time": 734658.0,
      "text": "This means more wealth distributed to all of us"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 734658.0,
      "end_time": 737189.0,
      "text": "and a better future for our children."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 737189.0,
      "end_time": 738374.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 738374.0,
      "end_time": 748374.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}